VI) A) Look at the following pictures and make sentences in the example :
  1) Brush three times a day = ichi nichi ni sankai ha o migakimasu
  2) sleep seven hours a day = ichi nichi ni shichi jikan nemasu
  3) study three hours a day = ichi nichi ni san ji kan benkyou shimasu
  4) clean the room once a week = i-shuu kan ni i-ka iheya o souji shimasu
  5) do laundry twice a week = i-shuu kan ni ni kai sentaku shimasu
  6) work part-time three days a week = i-shuu kan ni mi-ka arubaito o shimasu
  7) go to school five days a week = i-shuu kan ni itsu kaga-kou ni iki masu
  8) go to watch a movie once a month = i-ka getsu ni i-kai eiga o mi ni ikimasu
